      "id": 845661,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "A typo in the permissions mechanism for `/api/apps/logs` and `/api/apps/:id/logs` allows any authenticated user to retrieve information via GET requests.\n\nAffects versions <8.4.0, <8.3.2, <8.2.2, <8.1.3, <8.0.4, <7.13.6, <7.12.7, <7.11.7, and <7.10.10.",
